Subject: Re: [T2] Valve cover gasket sealer?

--- David Brooks <brooksdj(-at-)earthlink.net> wrote:

> What does everyone use on the valve cover side of
> the gasket. anything at all?<<

I dip my finger in a tub of grease and spread just
enough on the valve cover side of the gasket to make
it "wet".  I honestly don't know if this helps or not,
but I read somewhere to do it, and I have never had a
leak from the valve cover in my bus.


